data.description: This stunning home features stunning wood-style vinyl plank flooring throughout all of the main living areas of the home. The entry hallway opens to a huge great room, kitchen and dining space. This area features volume ceilings and tons of natural light from the windows and a sliding glass door that leads to the covered back patio. The upgraded kitchen includes Silestone® countertops in Charcoal Soapstone, an island, cabinets in Cotton color and stainless steel appliances by Whirlpool®. The master suite is located at the back of the home for a quiet retreat and offers a huge walk-in closet. The master bath boasts beautiful custom tile flooring, an enlarged walk-in shower with tile surround and a dual-sink vanity. This community has direct access to South Lake Trail for biking, walking and running.
